Current buzzwords or highest searched phrases (BUZZ)
----------------------------------------------------
   Displays top 10 buzzwords/keywords/phrases.

   Most searched keywords on Google.

   Data could be mined from Hitwise or FB.

   Users able to customize the buzzwords/keywords/phrases they are monitoring to
      know the size of the population searching those words

   Probably lock it to an industry or vertical

   List of keywords can be obtained from Hitwise, twitter trends, google trends,
      yahoo trends
